---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Digestive Harmony | Digestive Health Education</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Digestive Harmony is a nonprofit organization supporting digestive health education, awareness, and community." />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo">Digestive Harmony</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/blog">Resources</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <p class="eyebrow">Digestive Health | Education | Community</p>
          <h1>Helping people understand digestive health with clarity and compassion.</h1>
          <p>
            Digestive Harmony is a nonprofit organization dedicated to education,
            awareness, and support for individuals and families affected by digestive conditions.
          </p>
          <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/about">Our Mission</a>
            <a class="secondary" href="/blog">Explore Resources</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <h3>Reliable. Compassionate. Accessible.</h3>
          <p>
            We help simplify digestive health information so patients, caregivers,
            and families can feel more informed and less alone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Our Focus</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that education can reduce fear, improve confidence, and help people
          take meaningful steps toward better digestive wellness.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="cards">
        <article>
          <span>01</span>
          <h3>Digestive Disorders</h3>
          <p>Educational resources on IBS, IBD, GERD, Crohn's disease, ulcerative colitis, celiac disease, and more.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <span>02</span>
          <h3>Nutrition & Lifestyle</h3>
          <p>Simple, practical guidance for gut-friendly food choices, wellness habits, and daily digestive support.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <span>03</span>
          <h3>Patient Education</h3>
          <p>Clear articles, guides, and resources designed to make digestive health easier to understand.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <span>04</span>
          <h3>Community Support</h3>
          <p>Helping patients, caregivers, and families feel connected, informed, and supported.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="cta">
        <h2>Building a healthier, more informed community.</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you are a patient, caregiver, volunteer, or healthcare advocate,
          Digestive Harmony welcomes you.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact">Get Involved</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 Digestive Harmony. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --teal: #1f7a70;
    --dark: #173b3f;
    --light: #eefaf7;
    --soft: #f7fffd;
    --gold: #d8a84f;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    color: var(--dark);
    background: var(--soft);
  }

  header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 22px 8%;
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  nav a {
    margin-left: 26px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--dark);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 95px 8%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, #dff7f1, transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #eefaf7, #ffffff);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 58px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 18px 0;
    max-width: 850px;
  }

  .hero-text p {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .buttons {
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .buttons a,
  .cta a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 26px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--teal);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-right: 12px;
  }

  .buttons .secondary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--teal);
    border: 1px solid var(--teal);
  }

  .hero-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(31, 122, 112, 0.14);
    border-top: 6px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-card h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .hero-card p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 70px 8% 30px;
  }

  .intro h2,
  .cta h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .intro p,
  .cta p {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: auto;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 40px 8% 90px;
  }

  article {
    background: white;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  article span {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  article h3 {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 23px;
  }

  article p {
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .cta {
    margin: 0 8% 80px;
    padding: 60px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 34px;
  }

  .cta a {
    margin-top: 28px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px;
    background: white;
    color: #5d7375;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    header {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav {
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    nav a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 8px;
    }

    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 70px 6%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 30px 6% 70px;
    }
  }
</style>
